This class implements the Serializable aspect of the Common.Iterator.IPositionableIterator by extending Common.Serialization.Serializable. Concrete implementations of IPositionableIterator that wish to use Common.Serialization.Serializable can extend this class, rather than extending both IPositionableIterator and Common.Serialization.Serializable.
